            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tlamantli mozaico tlachihualli ica ihhuitl tlen tlamahchihchihualli ica altepetzitzin nahuatl. Tlamantli quence tlaquemitl, betarol huan chimalli.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Eastern Huasteca Nahuatl</Note_Language>
